- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a deep neural network model for predicting information diffusion using supervised learning.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with information spread and evolution in a network of users and repositories.
- cs.DL (Deep Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a deep neural network model for predicting information diffusion.
